listitem.extension:
f(x)=\begin{cases}
1 \text{ if }x=0\\
\frac{1}{q}\text{ if }x=\frac{p}{q}\text{(in lowest terms) is a rational number}\\
 0\text{ if }x\text{ is irrational}.
\end{cases}

D(x)=\begin{cases}
 0\text{ if }x\text{ is irrational } (\in \mathbb{R} \setminus \mathbb{Q})\\
 1\text{ if }x\text{ is rational } (\in \mathbb{Q})
\end{cases}
